---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import CallToAction from "@components/CallToAction.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="mx-32">
    <h1 class="text-center text-6xl font-bold leading-tight my-32">Services</h1>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Does This Sound Like You?</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
        <li>
          Are you trying to stay healthy and fit but can't because of pain
          stopping you from exercising?
        </li>
        <li>
          Are you worried that an injury will stop you from participating in
          activities you love, like CrossFit, weightlifting, surfing, or
          running?
        </li>
        <li>
          Have you been dealing with a chronic injury that just hasn't gone
          away?
        </li>
        <li>
          Have you seen other medical providers in the past with no long-lasting
          change in your pain?
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p class="mb-6">
        <span class="font-bold">Performance Based Therapy</span>
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">
        We will work with you to determine the root cause of your problem, work
        with you to solve the problem, and show you how to fix the problem for
        good. We incorporate movement/mobility drills, prescriptive exercise
        programming, and progressive loading to "lock in" improvements.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">
        We have worked with 1000's of athletes just like you to help them
        progress from frustrated, painful, and hopeless to pain-free,
        progressing like they want, and hitting new PR's in a matter of weeks!
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <div class="mt-32 w-fit mx-auto">
    <CallToAction />
  </div>
</Layout>
